<mj-section>
  <mj-column>
    <mj-text
      font-size="24px"
      font-weight="bold"
      color="#4a4a4a"
      align="center"
      padding-bottom="20px"
    >
      Two-Factor Authentication 🔒
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text> Hey {{name}}! 👋 </mj-text>

    <mj-text>
      Looks like you're trying to log in to your Minova account with two-factor authentication.
      Extra security for the win!
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text font-size="20px" font-weight="bold" align="center" padding="20px 0">
      Here's your magic code: <span style="color: #f7b801">{{token}}</span> ✨
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text>
      Just pop this code into the login screen to finish signing in. It'll expire in 10 minutes, so
      don't wait too long! ⏱️
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text>
      Didn't try to log in? Better change your password right away to keep your account safe.
    </mj-text>
  </mj-column>
</mj-section>
